Summary:
In this issue I can bypass Captcha Protection in the Forgot Password form.

Steps to Reproduce:
1. Enter your email id in the forgot password parameter.
2. Complete the captcha.
3. Capture the request in the proxy (Burp, ZAP)).
4. Delete captcha parameter from request.

